{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defeat your opponents at the card table and uncover their secrets!</h2>TCA is a political, humorous card adventure game with charm. Discover the atmospheric (ballpoint pen) hand-drawn world and its inhabitants and collect lots of cards in the process! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/walkingGif.gif?t=1738933549\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collect cards and build a deck!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/Trash_Cards_14.08.2024_16_33_52.png?t=1738933549\" /><br>Choose from many cards with different values and abilities to build your own deck!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Talk to characters and learn dark truths</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/Trash_Cards_14.08.2024_16_50_18.png?t=1738933549\" /><br>What lies behind the fa\u00e7ade of the cozy small town? A demonic rat, a cult in the sewers and the impending end of the world. In between, the everyday madness of the present.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find your very own strategy</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/extras/Trash_Cards_14.08.2024_16_54_31.png?t=1738933549\" /><br>Not every strategy leads to the goal. Combine different card types or specialize!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738933549","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/page.bg.jpg?t=1738933549","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/4959d86a19f32fa0409ee6e201f704394fb879f1/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738933549","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169850/4959d86a19f32fa0409ee6e201f704394fb